<header><div id="header-title"><h1>Visit New York City</h1>
<h2> The largest city in America. Times Square, Broadway, and much more await you. </h2>
</div>

<span class="header-pics"><div id="header-pic1"><a target="_blank" href="../images/nyc3.jpg" title="New York City, USA">
<img src="../thumbnails/nyc3.jpg" alt="NYC3"></a></div>
<div id="header-pic2"><a target="_blank" href="../images/nyc4.jpg" title="New York City, USA">
