<div class="reviewandresponse"><div class="review"><b><p><q>Dazzling</q></p></b>

<font size = "2"><p>by Chris K, Written September 19, 2015 </p></font>

<p> <b> Rating:</b> 5/5 </p>

<p> An absolute assault on the senses, but you just have to go here if you are in New York! It is a
real mecca, and is surrounded by great bars and restaurants, but you can just sit and watch life go
by at a multitude of paces whilst taking in the view. Stay as long or as short as you want, it does
not matter. You will feel amazed!</p></div>

